WinCacheU_FileAndUserCacheScenario, WinCacheU_OnlyFileCacheScenario, WinCacheU_OnlyUserCacheScenario
public abstract class WinCacheUScenario
extends UserCacheScenario

Using only the user, object and file caching components of WinCache, NOT the code caching. Can be used with Opcache just like APCU (but its designed for Windows, so for CLI and IIS scenarios, WinCacheU+Opcache will work a lot better than Opcache+APCU).
